<li><a href="/wiki/Bazooka" title="Bazooka">Rocket Launcher, M1/A1 "Bazooka"</a> <i>(U.S <a href="/wiki/Lend_Lease" title="Lend Lease" class="mw-redirect">Lend Lease</a>)</i>, Nationalist</li>
</ul>
